'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2411] on 18 June 2000 at 6:31:09 pm'!"Change Set:		161WeekDayFix-rcaDate:			15 June 2000Author:			Russell AllenToday was apparently day 0 according to the weekdayIndex (which sounds rather ominous).Here is a fix so that the proper weekday is returned."!!Date methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'rca 6/15/2000 14:51'!weekdayIndex	"Monday=1, ... , Sunday=7"	^ (self julianDayNumber rem: 7) + 1! !